Hank Harris https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hank_Harris 0 Hank Harris (born November 5, 1979) is an American actor who has been working in movies and television since the late 1990s. He grew up in Duluth, Minnesota and Santa Fe, New Mexico. He is perhaps best known for his role as Emory Dick in Popular. His other projects have included: Mercury Rising, Pumpkin, Hellbent and the television series Dirty Work.
